description: Increases all party members' DEF by 35%, lasting for 30m. (This effect only applies to your own Resonator(s) in Co-op Mode)
bgDescription: A snack popular among the children of Jinzhou, made with deep-fried meat bits of starry shapes and served with a special power dip. It is said that you can make a wish after eating it. "One star, two stars... you can't make a wish without eating it!"
